&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Travel as needed, including some weekends, evenings, or overnights for conferences, meetings, or special events. Expectation for ~75% travel or field time. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
